@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam dpi 180
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 16
skinparam defaultFontColor #1F2937
skinparam ArrowColor #315780
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.6
skinparam activityBorderColor #315780
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #315780
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #E9F0F7
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F3F7FA
skinparam noteBorderColor #8496A8
skinparam titleFontColor #17324D
skinparam titleFontSize 24

title Reliable order lifecycle

start
:Receive typed trading proposal;
:Validate the response schema;

if (Schema valid?) then (Yes)
  :Calculate neutral consequences;
  :Perform one final model review;
else (No)
  :Record incident and default to HOLD;
  stop
endif

if (Action approved?) then (Yes)
  :Run operational checks;
else (No)
  :Persist the decision without execution;
  stop
endif

if (Operationally valid?) then (Yes)
  :Create deterministic order identity;
  :Persist intent before submission;
else (No)
  :Block the invalid operation;
  stop
endif

:Submit the signed order once;
:Reconcile acknowledgement and fills\nwith the exchange;
:Persist protections, fees, funding\nand net P&L;
:Expose the complete audit trail;
stop

note right
  Core guarantees
  • strict typed contracts
  • durable intent before submission
  • stable client order identity
  • reconciliation instead of blind retry
end note
@enduml
